c: 48
v: 6
t: "Ne abahelesie eshinyasio abeshikhabili, abasatsa nabakhasi, nende abatsokasinjia Nyasaye abasatsa nabakhasi abapariranga Nyasaye amaparo amabii, kuliboolela omukalukhano omubii, Ne Nyasaye yabasinyishila,\tmana\tnabatsuba, nenabarecheshela omulilo kwa Jahannam, ne ni amakalushilo amabii muno"